<item>
            <title>[HBASE-13707] CellCounter uses to many counters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-13707</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CellCounters creates a counter per row... So it quickly becomes to many.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should provide an option to drop the statistic per rows and count only cells overall for the table.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12830815">HBASE-13707</key>
            <summary>CellCounter uses to many counters</summary>
